DataTypes
description:
Google::Monitoring::V3

Class Description
Google::Monitoring::V3::Aggregation Describes how to combine multiple time series to provide different views of the data.
Google::Monitoring::V3::Aggregation::Aligner The Aligner describes how to bring the data points in a single time series into temporal alignment.
Google::Monitoring::V3::Aggregation::Reducer A Reducer describes how to aggregate data points from multiple time series into a single time series.
Google::Monitoring::V3::Group The description of a dynamic collection of monitored resources.
Google::Monitoring::V3::Point A single data point in a time series.
Google::Monitoring::V3::TimeInterval A time interval extending just after a start time through an end time.
Google::Monitoring::V3::TimeSeries A collection of data points that describes the time-varying values of a metric.
Google::Monitoring::V3::TypedValue A single strongly-typed value.

Google::Api

Class Description
Google::Api::Distribution Distribution contains summary statistics for a population of values and, optionally, a histogram representing the distribution of those values across a specified set of histogram buckets.
Google::Api::Distribution::BucketOptions A Distribution may optionally contain a histogram of the values in the population.
Google::Api::Distribution::BucketOptions::Explicit A set of buckets with arbitrary widths.
Google::Api::Distribution::BucketOptions::Exponential Specify a sequence of buckets that have a width that is proportional to the value of the lower bound.
Google::Api::Distribution::BucketOptions::Linear Specify a sequence of buckets that all have the same width (except overflow and underflow).
Google::Api::Distribution::Range The range of the population values.
Google::Api::LabelDescriptor A description of a label.
Google::Api::LabelDescriptor::ValueType Value types that can be used as label values.
Google::Api::Metric A specific metric, identified by specifying values for all of the labels of a +MetricDescriptor+.
Google::Api::MetricDescriptor Defines a metric type and its schema.
Google::Api::MetricDescriptor::MetricKind The kind of measurement.
Google::Api::MetricDescriptor::ValueType The value type of a metric.
Google::Api::MonitoredResource An object representing a resource that can be used for monitoring, logging, billing, or other purposes.
Google::Api::MonitoredResourceDescriptor An object that describes the schema of a MonitoredResource object using a type name and a set of labels.

Google::Protobuf

Class Description
Google::Protobuf::Duration A Duration represents a signed, fixed-length span of time represented as a count of seconds and fractions of seconds at nanosecond resolution.
Google::Protobuf::Timestamp A Timestamp represents a point in time independent of any time zone or calendar, represented as seconds and fractions of seconds at nanosecond resolution in UTC Epoch time.
